  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and bell pepper and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the ground beef and cook until browned, breaking it up into small pieces as it cooks.",
    "Add the fajita seasoning, cumin, smoked paprika, and tunisian harissa, and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the shredded cabbage and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
